snippet: Dirk Nowitzki scored 31 points, Deron Williams had 10 of his 20 points in overtime and the Dallas Mavericks beat the Boston Celtics 118-113 on Monday night....
lead_paragraph: Dirk Nowitzki scored 31 points, Deron Williams had 10 of his 20 points in overtime and the Dallas Mavericks beat the Boston Celtics 118-113 on Monday night.

headline.main: Nowitzki, Williams Lead Mavericks Past Celtics 118-113 in OT
headline.print_headline: Nowitzki, Williams Lead Mavericks Past Celtics 118-113 in OT
